00:49:42.840 --> 00:49:51.180
let me begin by reading a
short passage from a book that

00:49:51.180 --> 00:49:56.510
was published over 100 years
ago by Rabindranath Tagore.

00:49:56.510 --> 00:49:59.850
And towards the
end of that book,

00:49:59.850 --> 00:50:05.370
in an essay titled
"Nationalism in India",

00:50:05.370 --> 00:50:09.600
Tagore said a few things
both about the United States

00:50:09.600 --> 00:50:14.880
and India that sound like
an uncanny foretelling

00:50:14.880 --> 00:50:19.990
of the crises that both
our countries face today.

00:50:19.990 --> 00:50:23.340
So Tagore criticized the
anti-Asiatic agitations

00:50:23.340 --> 00:50:26.940
in America for depriving
the aliens of their right

00:50:26.940 --> 00:50:30.270
to earn their honest
living on these shores.

00:50:30.270 --> 00:50:33.180
Either you shut your
doors against the aliens

00:50:33.180 --> 00:50:38.400
or reduce them into slavery,
Tagore said in his rebuke.

00:50:38.400 --> 00:50:40.110
And he had something
even more perceptive

00:50:40.110 --> 00:50:44.160
and far sighted to say about the
tyranny of social restrictions

00:50:44.160 --> 00:50:45.780
in India.

00:50:45.780 --> 00:50:48.330
The social habit
of mind, he wrote,

00:50:48.330 --> 00:50:52.230
which impels us to make the life
of our fellow beings a burden

00:50:52.230 --> 00:50:55.200
to them, where they
differ from us even

00:50:55.200 --> 00:50:57.720
in such a thing as
their choice of food,

00:50:57.720 --> 00:51:00.960
is sure to persist in our
political organizatio.

00:51:00.960 --> 00:51:04.260
And result in creating
engines of coercion

00:51:04.260 --> 00:51:06.750
to crush every rational
difference, which

00:51:06.750 --> 00:51:08.580
is the sign of life.

00:51:08.580 --> 00:51:13.530
And tyranny will only add to the
inevitable lies and hypocrisy

00:51:13.530 --> 00:51:16.050
in our political life.

00:51:16.050 --> 00:51:24.910
Now I entered Parliament
on an unhappy day,

00:51:24.910 --> 00:51:29.300
the 16th of May 2014.

00:51:29.300 --> 00:51:32.880
That was the day
