May 2014, he would

00:52:07.470 --> 00:52:12.510
drive all illegal
immigrants across the border

00:52:12.510 --> 00:52:14.560
of Bangladesh.

00:52:14.560 --> 00:52:19.140
Modi had spoken about
illegal immigrants

00:52:19.140 --> 00:52:23.880
two years before Trump did
more or less the same thing

00:52:23.880 --> 00:52:28.560
during his campaign in 2016.

00:52:28.560 --> 00:52:32.610
I gave my first
speech in Parliament

00:52:32.610 --> 00:52:35.670
on the same day
