00:52:55.410 --> 00:52:57.810
But this is what happened.

00:52:57.810 --> 00:53:00.720
As I said, we mourn the
death of Mohsin Shaikh

00:53:00.720 --> 00:53:03.450
the young computer
engineer in Pune.

00:53:03.450 --> 00:53:06.180
He belonged to the
so-called aspirational class

00:53:06.180 --> 00:53:09.690
whose dreams for the future
had been fired by the election

00:53:09.690 --> 00:53:11.940
campaign of the ruling party.

00:53:11.940 --> 00:53:14.130
He did not live to
see the [NON-ENGLISH],,

00:53:14.130 --> 00:53:17.340
the good times which this
government promises to usher

00:53:17.340 --> 00:53:18.180
in.

00:53:18.180 --> 00:53:22.440
His only fault was that he wore
his identity in his headgear

00:53:22.440 --> 00:53:27.120
and attire as he returned home
after praying to the almighty.

00:53:27.120 --> 00:53:29.700
Hockey sticks that had
once done our nation

00:53:29.700 --> 00:53:32.100
proud in the world
of sports were

00:53:32.100 --> 00:53:38.280
used as weapons to bludgeon
the expression of diversity.

00:53:38.280 --> 00:53:42.570
Now after that, of course, there
were several other incidents

00:53:42.570 --> 00:53:44.340
of lynching.

00:53:44.340 --> 00:53:52.800
And what I would say is that the
one that was not specifically

00:53:52.800 --> 00:53:57.270
