by writers and scholars

00:54:12.120 --> 00:54:15.180
and so on that there was
a debate in Parliament

00:54:15.180 --> 00:54:18.720
on quote unquote "growing
intolerance in India."

00:54:18.720 --> 00:54:21.340
And the term intolerance
