citizenship certainly

01:01:42.830 --> 01:01:48.130
out of constitutional
discourse to actually justify

01:01:48.130 --> 01:01:53.020
the complicitors' notions
of discrimination.

01:01:53.020 --> 01:01:56.510
And beyond discrimination
also degradation.

01:01:56.510 --> 01:01:58.340
And they're not the same thing.

01:01:58.340 --> 01:01:59.810
They can come together.

01:01:59.810 --> 01:02:04.010
Very often discrimination
is thought of within a kind

01:02:04.010 --> 01:02:05.420
of legal imaginary.

01:02:05.420 --> 01:02:09.890
But with the right politics
and with the right agitation

01:02:09.890 --> 01:02:12.210
and if we move to
the law, the law

01:02:12.210 --> 01:02:14.460
can get rid of discrimination.

