01:02:24.220 --> 01:02:31.280
impurity, criminality, rape
both in the United States

01:02:31.280 --> 01:02:32.960
as well as in India.

01:02:32.960 --> 01:02:38.060
The language of denigration,
the dedignified language

01:02:38.060 --> 01:02:43.490
of denigration is now taking
on a power beyond any appeal

01:02:43.490 --> 01:02:45.710
to the citizen and
the non-citizen.

01:02:45.710 --> 01:02:48.050
And this is why I think
the migrant or the refugee

01:02:48.050 --> 01:02:51.985
becomes such a problematic
flashpoint in this discourse.

01:02:51.985 --> 01:02:54.110
As the president of the
ruling party recently said,

01:02:54.110 --> 01:02:56.151
we have a billion termites
in our country who are

01:02:56.151 --> 01:02:57.920
sort of hollowing it through.

01:02:57.920 --> 01:03:00.290
So I will address the
question of constitutionalism.

