01:42:23.500 --> 01:42:24.640
No.

01:42:24.640 --> 01:42:25.390
You're right.

01:42:25.390 --> 01:42:28.070
It doesn't lead to
specific conclusions.

01:42:28.070 --> 01:42:31.070
And I think you're also--

01:42:31.070 --> 01:42:32.590
Let us first be
