01:44:20.880 --> 01:44:22.900
it is the duty to bring it out.

01:44:22.900 --> 01:44:25.330
So the idea of actually
doing it in this form

01:44:25.330 --> 01:44:28.210
was so that it insulates it
from this kind of criticism

01:44:28.210 --> 01:44:29.950
