You can't dispute that.

01:44:38.470 --> 01:44:41.230
So I think let's not
reduce everything

01:44:41.230 --> 01:44:44.410
to these easy social
media binaries.

01:44:44.410 --> 01:44:48.670
Let's try to look at things,
you know, truths or facts,

01:44:48.670 --> 01:44:50.720
as they are on
their own standing.

01:44:50.720 --> 01:44:52.600
So I mean, I really urge that.

01:44:52.600 --> 01:44:53.390
Thank you.

