01:46:49.000 --> 01:46:52.540
One is it's either a
new religion, which

01:46:52.540 --> 01:46:54.910
is like you're talking
about revival in religion.

01:46:54.910 --> 01:46:58.720
Or the second is a
revolt. And that's

01:46:58.720 --> 01:47:00.430
where I think where
Pakistan comes from

01:47:00.430 --> 01:47:01.630
is a state of revolt.

01:47:01.630 --> 01:47:03.520
But I mean, I don't know
where we are headed.

