Homi, sorry, can I just
on the fake news point.

01:52:00.080 --> 01:52:03.340
While I agree that
self-regulation is important,

01:52:03.340 --> 01:52:07.740
but at the same time it's not as
if you can just let claims also

01:52:07.740 --> 01:52:08.910
go uncontested.

01:52:08.910 --> 01:52:12.270
For instance, what you
just saw was an example

01:52:12.270 --> 01:52:14.960
of busting of fake news as in
the case of the Meerat Love

01:52:14.960 --> 01:52:15.900
Jihad case, right?

01:52:15.900 --> 01:52:19.860
So something like that, a
completely manufactured fiction

01:52:19.860 --> 01:52:22.830
about gang rape and
maulanas and so on has

01:52:22.830 --> 01:52:25.480
the potential to create
social unrest, which it did.

01:52:25.480 --> 01:52:28.620
And the busting of it
does help in some cases

01:52:28.620 --> 01:52:29.550
to cool things down.

01:52:29.550 --> 01:52:34.030
So I don't think it's
about ignoring fake news.

01:52:34.030 --> 01:52:36.510
It's about what fake news
is that you choose to bust.

01:52:36.510 --> 01:52:39.900
If you want to sit and go after
every single WhatsApp forward,

01:52:39.900 --> 01:52:40.920
there is no end to it.

01:52:40.920 --> 01:52:43.780
But certainly the most
egregious examples,

01:52:43.780 --> 01:52:46.680
especially when the state lies
or the state is putting out

01:52:46.680 --> 01:52:53.520
false claims or propaganda or of
this kind of incendiary stuff,

01:52:53.520 --> 01:52:56.860
I think there it's important
to actually come out and do it.

01:52:56.860 --> 01:52:59.850
And to your point as to what
should be done, as you probably

01:52:59.850 --> 01:53:02.190
know in the Indian context
and the world over,

01:53:02.190 --> 01:53:04.470
increasingly news
organizations are

01:53:04.470 --> 01:53:09.400
investing huge amounts of
resources to busting fake news.

01:53:09.400 --> 01:53:11.941
So that's already
organically happening.

01:53:11.941 --> 01:53:13.440
There are mainstream
media doing it,

01:53:13.440 --> 01:53:15.930
there are all sorts of
websites and portals doing it.

01:53:15.930 --> 01:53:18.530
And you know, I think
that's a good thing.

01:53:18.530 --> 01:53:20.250
Except because that
fake news seems

01:53:20.250 --> 01:53:24.870
to be more attractive
than factual news.

01:53:24.870 --> 01:53:26.182
People love fake news.

01:53:26.182 --> 01:53:27.390
I mean, it's not for nothing.

01:53:27.390 --> 01:53:28.110
It's more entertaining.

01:53:28.110 --> 01:53:29.068
It's more entertaining.

